Sixplay is the Sixaxis Joystick Manager
 -----------------------------------

In order to build, install and use sixplay you'll need:

1 - Compile sixplay: (dev packages)
----> libusb
----> libbluetooth3
----> libdbus-1
----> libdbus-glib-1
----> libjack (optional, for sixplay-jack)

2 - Use sixplay:
----> bluez (recent versions are recommended)
----> libbluetooth3
----> udev (optional, automatically starts sixplay when needed)


================================================================================

To install all the stuff, just do:

cd /path/to/extracted/src
make
sudo make install
sudo make install-system


^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

Sixplay has been tested (and proved to work) in:
- ArchLinux


